{"word":"G2270 - ἡσυχάζω - hēsycházō - hay-soo-khad'-zo - Cease","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἡσυχάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hēsycházō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hay-soo-khad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cease</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பேசாமல் இரு, ஓய்ந்திரு, அமைதியாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to keep quiet, to rest, to cease from labor"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G2272 - ἡσύχιος - hēsýchios - hay-soo'-khee-os/2272\">G2272</a>; to <i>keep still</i> (intransitively), that is, <i>refrain</i> from labor, meddlesomeness or speech: - cease, hold peace, be quiet, rest.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}